<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=7225f0f4a749283da29a7362&lemmaId=125079&lemmaId=125079&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">一曲《钗头凤》，让陆游变成情种？</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2018-06-05 22:06</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>“生命诚可贵，爱情价更高。”唐婉就是因为把爱情当成了生命的全部，所以，写了和词之后不久就抑郁而终了。可怜的唐婉，“雨送黄昏花易落”，这朵柔弱的花朵，为何不能迎着阳光勇敢地挑战命运，为何不能去寻找新的爱情重新来过？</span><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=7225f0f4a749283da29a7362&lemmaId=125079&lemmaId=125079&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
