</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type3 more" id="reference-[93]-2370-wrap">
<span class="index">93.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_93_2370" id="refIndex_93_2370" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[93]_2370">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<span class="text">陈衍《宋诗精华录》</span>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type3 more" id="reference-[94]-2370-wrap">
<span class="index">94.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_94_2370" id="refIndex_94_2370" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[94]_2370">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<span class="text">陆游《白鹤馆夜坐》：袖手哦新诗，清寒愧雄浑。屈宋死千载，谁能起九原？中间李与杜，独招湘水魂。自此竞摹写，几人望其藩？兰苕看翡翠，烟雨啼青猿。岂知云海中，九万击鹏鲲。</span>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type3 more" id="reference-[95]-2370-wrap">
<span class="index">95.</span>
