<span class="text">陆游《秋怀十首》：永怀杜拾遗，抱病起登台。</span>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type3 more" id="reference-[98]-2370-wrap">
<span class="index">98.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_98_2370" id="refIndex_98_2370" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[98]_2370">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<span class="text">陆游《示子遹》：我初学诗日，但欲工藻绘；中年始少悟，渐若窥宏大。</span>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type3 more" id="reference-[99]-2370-wrap">
<span class="index">99.</span>
