<span class="index">108.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_108_2370" id="refIndex_108_2370" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[108]_2370">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<span class="text">刘熙载《艺概·诗概》</span>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type3 more" id="reference-[109]-2370-wrap">
<span class="index">109.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_109_2370" id="refIndex_109_2370" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[109]_2370">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<span class="text">陆游《九日春阴一日晴》为晚清画家钱慧安绘。</span>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type3 more" id="reference-[110]-2370-wrap">
<span class="index">110.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_110_2370" id="refIndex_110_2370" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[110]_2370">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<span class="text">桑叶按：陆游认为词是“其变愈薄”之体，说“少时汩于世俗，颇有所为，晚而悔之”。写了词，仿佛有种负罪感，故自编词集时，特意写上一段自我批评，“以志吾过”。这种陈旧的观念，既限制了词作的数量，更影响了其词的艺术质量和成就。</span>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type3 more" id="reference-[111]-2370-wrap">
<span class="index">111.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_111_2370" id="refIndex_111_2370" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[111]_2370">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<span class="text">陆游《汉宫春》：羽箭雕弓，忆呼鹰古垒，截虎平川。吹笳暮归，野帐雪压青毡。淋漓醉墨，看龙蛇、飞落蛮笺。人误许，诗情将略，一时才气超然。</span>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type3 more" id="reference-[112]-2370-wrap">
<span class="index">112.</span>
