<span class="index">149.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_149_2370" id="refIndex_149_2370" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[149]_2370">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<span>蒋凡、白振奎</span><span class="text">．《陆游集》</span><span>：凤凰出版社</span><span>，2006</span></li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type2 more" id="reference-[150]-2370-wrap">
<span class="index">150.</span>
